              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "Based on average daily sales so far in 2023, we believe",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontFamily": "DIN",
                      "fontSize": "16pt",
                      "color": "#ffffff"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": " $ 1,409,207",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "fontFamily": "DIN",
                      "fontSize": "16pt",
                      "color": "#efb251"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": " is a reasonable target for our first year of sales across our 3 Florida locations",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontFamily": "DIN",
                      "fontSize": "16pt",
                      "color": "#ffffff"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": ""
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "However, this does not fully account for the great momentum that we have seen in May and June of this year. Notice on the right that ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontFamily": "DIN",
                      "fontSize": "16pt",
                      "color": "#ffffff"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "average daily sales for January-March were only ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "fontFamily": "DIN",
                      "fontSize": "16pt",
                      "color": "#efb251"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": {
                      "propertyIdentifier": {
                        "objectName": "values",
                        "propertyName": "expr"
                      },
                      "selector": {
                        "id": "Value"
                      }
                    },
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "fontFamily": "DIN",
                      "fontSize": "16pt",
                      "color": "#efb251"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": " while ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontFamily": "DIN",
                      "fontSize": "16pt",
                      "color": "#ffffff"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "average daily sales for April-June spiked to ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "fontFamily": "DIN",
                      "fontSize": "16pt",
                      "color": "#efb251"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": {
                      "propertyIdentifier": {
                        "objectName": "values",
                        "propertyName": "expr"
                      },
                      "selector": {
                        "id": "Value 2"
                      }
                    },
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "fontFamily": "DIN",
                      "fontSize": "16pt",
                      "color": "#efb251"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": ".",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontFamily": "DIN",
                      "fontSize": "16pt",
                      "color": "#ffffff"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": ""
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "If we can sustain that exceptional growth, we fell confident that our new offices can help us  blow the above sales target out of the water (yes, that's a nautical pun). Even though the above number is our goal, we would be thrilled to see our 3 ne Florida offices hit our stretch goal of ",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontFamily": "DIN",
                      "fontSize": "16pt",
                      "color": "#ffffff"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "$ 1,592,839",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold",
                      "fontFamily": "DIN",
                      "fontSize": "16pt",
                      "color": "#efb251"
                    }
                  },
                  {
